    "body": "@zcbenz I get that we are just a thin wrapper over native GUI APIs but this is proving a rather annoying issue for us in automated testing.\n\nWe are using spectron and calling `setSize`; on Windows the test passes as the size is truncated at the minimum and max values.\n\nOn macOS it fails, this inconsistency is a bit annoying.  Can this be handled inside electron in anyway or do you think that test should be disabled on macOS?\n"
